About

Gardner Lewis Asset Management is a privately-owned investment management firm located outside of Philadelphia, PA.  Since the firm’s inception in 1990, the focus of the investment team has been to seek, identify and invest in compelling opportunities for both institutions and individuals throughout the United States and abroad.  The firm has been trusted to manage assets for respected corporations, foundations, endowments and individuals globally for over two decades.
What sets our firm apart?
Alignment of Interests

Independent firm owned entirely by its investment professionals – unencumbered by distractions associated with larger organizations.
We invest alongside our clients in every strategy.

Consistent Firm Leadership

Leadership has been in place for over 20 years.
Average tenure of senior professionals is more than 15 years.

Singular Investment Philosophy

We invest opportunistically in Transformational Change.
Focused on companies effecting disruptive innovation and those undergoing positive change as the result of a dynamic catalyst.

Integrated Research Approach

Fundamental, bottom-up analysis.
Portfolio managers, analysts and traders work together without compartmentalization.







 






